WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.880 --> 00:00:03.279
Good morning family, praise the Lord.

00:00:03.279 --> 00:00:11.272
I wanted to show you what the Lord did, and I believe this is a sign and a wonder for where we were.

00:00:11.816 --> 00:00:15.374
Look, I put dye in there and it dyed my hand blue.

00:00:16.035 --> 00:00:20.880
I just want to give God praise because of what He did.

00:00:20.880 --> 00:00:34.892
We were in severe drought here in Oklahoma—a bad drought—and it was starting to mount up to the point where there were fires and all kinds of stuff starting to happen going into the winter months.

00:00:37.415 --> 00:00:43.915
We don't get a lot of rain in the winter, and we don't get a lot of rain at this time of the year in November.

00:00:43.915 --> 00:00:54.346
But I set out and started praying over the weather back in October, speaking to the rain and calling it in.

00:00:54.608 --> 00:01:05.140
The Lord gave us an inch in 24 hours, and it's still going to rain all night tonight and all day tomorrow, which is amazing.

00:01:05.640 --> 00:01:23.159
In a 24-hour period, it filled up this gauge—five inches of rain—plus we got over an inch and a half, so six and a half inches of rain in less than 48 hours so far.

00:01:23.499 --> 00:01:24.909
We have more coming.

00:01:24.909 --> 00:01:30.340
God is exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:01:30.340 --> 00:01:32.347
That's the kind of God we serve.

00:01:32.347 --> 00:01:42.994
If you just believe, all you have to do is stretch out there and believe by faith that you receive, calling those things that be not as though they were, speaking to the circumstances to change.

00:01:43.445 --> 00:01:45.177
Look, this is fruit.

00:01:45.555 --> 00:01:50.419
This is cold rain; I can feel it, it's making my fingers numb.

00:01:50.759 --> 00:02:02.346
I just wanted to say all things are possible to him that believes.

00:02:02.346 --> 00:02:09.702
Don't give up on what you're believing for.

00:02:09.702 --> 00:02:21.538
This is just something simple, but to the farmers, this is a big deal.

00:02:21.538 --> 00:02:40.631
Five inches of rain fills up the ponds and the lakes and gets us through.

00:02:40.631 --> 00:02:58.869
We were going through a severe drought here in Oklahoma, but God can turn it around on a dime.

00:02:58.869 --> 00:03:16.1000
If you just believe Him for the supernatural, believe Him for over and above all that you dare ask or think.

00:03:16.1000 --> 00:03:31.748
We have more coming—six and a half inches, folks, that's a lot of rain in 48 hours.

00:03:31.748 --> 00:03:47.613
Look at what Jesus does; it's like it parked over us and was dumping.

00:03:47.613 --> 00:03:52.210
Glory to God.

00:03:52.210 --> 00:04:05.188
We just want to tell you all thank you for joining us.

00:04:12.260 --> 00:04:18.567
My wife is going to come on today and talk to you all; she has a word from the Lord.

00:04:18.567 --> 00:04:25.853
The Lord woke her up and she has been sitting on this for a little bit because she prays over it like me.

00:04:25.853 --> 00:04:42.039
But I told her it's time for her to share that word the Lord gave her.

00:04:42.039 --> 00:05:02.600
She's going to talk to you all now about this word; she has two amazing words.

00:05:02.600 --> 00:05:16.880
She'll talk today and tomorrow about the things the Lord has been revealing to her.

00:05:16.880 --> 00:05:25.140
We'll pray together, take communion, and believe God.

00:05:28.400 --> 00:05:38.814
The Lord said He wants us to start praying more, so we're going to pray for no rioting because I've seen some riots in the spirit.

00:05:43.500 --> 00:06:24.490
The Lord told me to come against this rioting about the election results, against the spirit of division and the spirit of Antichrist, that our nation will not fall toward rioting and pillaging and people will cool their jets and be at peace.

00:06:24.735 --> 00:06:48.471
I believe this is a sign that it's time for the rain of the Holy Spirit and a supernatural drink.

00:06:50.018 --> 00:06:53.546
I hope you're thirsty today because Jesus is ready to fill you.

00:06:53.546 --> 00:06:56.800
Glory to God.

00:06:56.800 --> 00:07:03.080
Let's go straight to my wife now.

00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:05.510
'Good morning family.

00:07:08.351 --> 00:07:21.511
I just wanted to come on and tell you this word the Lord spoke to me.

00:07:21.511 --> 00:07:40.160
It was in between my sleep and awake as I was waking up.

00:07:53.366 --> 00:08:01.600
He started speaking to me, and as I wrote, He paused until I could finish writing it down.

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:07.919
It was just flowing; it blessed me and I know it will bless you.

00:08:10.710 --> 00:08:28.360
He was showing me the ones He can trust more, He gives multiple endowments and can use them more.

00:08:28.600 --> 00:08:39.893
Then I saw a three-stranded cord: healing, glory, and prayer.

00:08:39.893 --> 00:08:52.800
Prayer must be a pillar, for it will sustain you.

00:08:52.800 --> 00:09:05.378
If you don't operate in a prayer gifting, who are you anyway?

00:09:05.378 --> 00:09:20.062
' The deeper you go with Me, the more I can use you.

00:09:20.062 --> 00:09:32.770
(I really like what you just said, I think you should emphasize that.

00:09:36.839 --> 00:09:55.226
) This is for every minister; this is for anybody who's called to the five-fold ministry to walk in the giftings He's called them to.

00:10:02.885 --> 00:10:16.880
What He's saying is the ones He can trust more, He gives multiple endowments and can use them more.

00:10:19.142 --> 00:10:41.280
I saw in the spirit a three-stranded cord intertwined like a rope, and the three-stranded cord was healing, glory, and prayer.

00:10:41.280 --> 00:10:55.806
He said prayer must be a pillar, for it will sustain you.

00:10:55.806 --> 00:11:14.200
If you don't operate in a prayer gifting, then who are you anyway?

00:11:14.200 --> 00:11:18.879
Prayer is your foundation.

00:11:18.879 --> 00:11:29.915
As He was speaking to me, I'm just trembling and shaking.

00:11:37.159 --> 00:11:43.976
I saw in the spirit that I was before His throne room.

00:11:44.925 --> 00:11:53.453
I felt His tangible presence fall on me.

00:11:53.453 --> 00:12:17.648
Then He said, 'The deeper you go with Me, the more I can use you, and the more I will require of you.

00:12:17.648 --> 00:12:41.895
For if you truly know My heart, you know if I can't move through you and get it out to others, then what use are you?

00:12:41.895 --> 00:13:28.440
' If you're asking for the Lord to use you and He puts an anointing on you, but He can't get it through you because you're in fear or unwilling to talk to that individual, then what use are you to Him?

00:13:28.440 --> 00:13:32.320
You're bottling it up.

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:47.460
Check your heart each and every day; this is vital for you in the coming days and always.

00:13:47.460 --> 00:13:52.800
It's for your protection.

00:14:00.184 --> 00:14:06.260
He will not be mocked; He will have a move and manifestation of His glory.

00:14:14.839 --> 00:14:21.905
Then He was talking about what the Lord told Brandon about the older generation going home—the greats.

00:14:21.905 --> 00:14:27.620
There's going to be a great baton passing.

00:14:27.800 --> 00:14:37.666
He said they have asked, but in their heart, they are tired.

00:14:37.666 --> 00:14:50.119
They use it as an excuse, and I'm tired of hearing it.

00:14:50.119 --> 00:15:05.613
If I can't move through you, I have no use of you.

00:15:05.613 --> 00:15:14.980
They've had long lives; this is a promotion.

00:15:14.980 --> 00:15:18.827
They are coming home.

00:15:18.827 --> 00:15:46.800
But they have begged Me to use them mightily, and they cannot ask the things they have asked then turn their back on Me.

00:15:46.800 --> 00:15:52.919
It's a stench to My nose.

00:15:57.360 --> 00:16:15.409
You can't ask Me to use you and ask for long life then withhold yourself from allowing Me to distribute the impartations.

00:16:17.390 --> 00:16:24.660
My gifts will not be held hostage.

00:16:24.660 --> 00:16:33.839
They either move with Me or I'm calling them home.

00:16:33.839 --> 00:16:35.373
They say, 'Why, Lord?

00:16:35.373 --> 00:16:43.583
Why do you want me to do that?

00:16:43.583 --> 00:16:48.977
' and I'm tired of it.

00:16:48.977 --> 00:16:58.076
Get in sync with Me or get off the boat.

00:16:58.076 --> 00:17:09.595
I'm not held back by age, race, or time.

00:17:09.595 --> 00:17:16.183
This is a mockery of My endowment.

00:17:16.183 --> 00:17:24.039
Think about what He just said.

00:17:24.039 --> 00:17:36.157
He's not moved by age, skin color, or time.

00:17:36.157 --> 00:17:49.164
If you say He can't use you because of your race, you're missing it.

00:17:49.164 --> 00:18:00.220
Man looks at dumb stuff, but God looks at the heart.

00:18:00.220 --> 00:18:09.924
Get in sync with Me or get off the boat.

00:18:09.924 --> 00:18:18.880
He'll use whoever will yield himself to Him.

00:18:18.880 --> 00:18:43.585
'Be careful what you ask for if you cannot be in sync with Me and check your pride at the door.

00:18:47.475 --> 00:19:00.060
If you question Me all along the way, then you shouldn't be asking for it.

00:19:00.060 --> 00:19:13.680
There's no time; I don't have time to keep explaining myself to My refiners.

00:19:13.680 --> 00:19:29.898
' I love that He referred to them as refiners—the ones who have been through that refining fire.

00:19:29.898 --> 00:19:44.338
'If I can't move through you, I have no more use of you.

00:19:44.338 --> 00:20:11.497
So be careful, daughter, what you ask for, because everything I endow I will place a demand on, not just for a measure of time.

00:20:11.497 --> 00:20:26.849
There's a greater purpose for My movement and the manifestation of My glory.

00:20:26.849 --> 00:20:36.395
The harvest is plenty and the laborers are few.

00:20:43.720 --> 00:20:46.497
Many have asked, I have given, and they withhold.

00:20:46.497 --> 00:20:50.559
This will not happen.

00:20:50.559 --> 00:20:54.506
Be quick to obey.

00:20:54.506 --> 00:21:10.070
Stay in sync with Me, do a heart check every day, and you'll be okay.

00:21:10.070 --> 00:21:30.360
Do not ask for it and then complain when I ask you to use it for a greater purpose.

00:21:30.360 --> 00:21:41.660
Why would I give a gift endowment and not use it mightily?

00:21:41.660 --> 00:21:55.060
What use is a tool if it runs away and hides itself from Me?

00:21:55.060 --> 00:22:16.040
Do not ask things of Me and then run from Me as Adam and Eve did.

00:22:16.040 --> 00:22:33.520
With long life I will satisfy you, they keep saying, but they aren't satisfying Me.

00:22:34.960 --> 00:22:38.710
I will not be mocked.

00:22:38.710 --> 00:23:03.720
' They are using that scripture against Him, saying, 'Lord, you said with long life You'll satisfy me,' but they're not satisfying the Lord.

00:23:11.799 --> 00:23:24.308
He's trying to do something through them to save humanity for these last days, and they are like a stone wall to Him.

00:23:24.308 --> 00:23:37.140
'You're quoting these scriptures at Me, but you're not satisfying Me.

00:23:51.309 --> 00:23:51.594
Do not ask for it and then complain when I ask you to use it.

00:23:51.594 --> 00:24:06.148
What use is a tool if it runs away and hides itself from Me?

00:24:13.240 --> 00:24:22.200
Do not ask things of Me and then run like Adam and Eve did.

00:24:22.200 --> 00:24:37.451
With long life I will satisfy you, they keep saying, but they aren't satisfying Me.

00:24:37.451 --> 00:24:41.544
I will not be mocked.

00:24:41.544 --> 00:24:59.529
Instead of asking for My help for healing, energy, or youth renewed like an eagle, they withhold themselves from Me.

00:24:59.529 --> 00:25:03.919
I'm tired, Lord, they say.

00:25:03.919 --> 00:25:06.780
Well, come home then.

00:25:06.780 --> 00:25:24.423
' Then I saw a marriage bed where a wife would say she's too tired.

00:25:25.690 --> 00:25:36.540
The deeper you go with Me, be careful and don't get burned.

00:25:36.540 --> 00:25:44.531
If you abide in Me and My words abide in you, ask what you will and it will be done for you.

00:25:44.531 --> 00:26:12.688
I was asking Him to pluck anything up in my heart that's bad and fix me, and He said, 'I know, daughter, you're good.

00:26:12.688 --> 00:26:27.794
I'm just telling you what I require of you so you know what you're getting into.

00:26:37.900 --> 00:26:38.210
I am not a fine-print God.

00:26:38.210 --> 00:26:41.851
' Think about that.

00:26:52.952 --> 00:27:00.670
He is bold; you don't have to guess what God's trying to tell you to do.

00:27:05.754 --> 00:27:17.360
You don't have to read fine print like you see on those cartoons or in the movies.

00:27:17.360 --> 00:27:25.990
God's word is bold, black and white.

00:27:35.480 --> 00:27:35.800
He said, 'I am not a fine-print God.

00:27:35.800 --> 00:27:45.680
I am El Shaddai, the all-consuming fire.

00:27:50.782 --> 00:27:56.340
The revival can't happen until my harvesters are ready.

00:27:56.340 --> 00:28:06.412
' He has to have us to bring in the harvest.

00:28:06.412 --> 00:28:24.060
He can't bring in the revival until His harvesters are ready.

00:28:24.060 --> 00:28:29.039
Are you getting ready?

00:28:29.039 --> 00:28:29.399
Are you sold out?

00:28:29.399 --> 00:28:37.219
'The revival cannot happen until My harvest is ready.

00:28:45.880 --> 00:28:46.920
Don't make excuses to Me.

00:28:46.920 --> 00:29:02.188
Ask Me to make a way for you if you need something.

00:29:02.188 --> 00:29:12.426
Don't ever come before Me and make excuses.

00:29:12.426 --> 00:29:16.1000
I will not be mocked.

00:29:16.1000 --> 00:29:20.534
If you don't ask, I can't give it to you.

00:29:22.044 --> 00:29:24.240
I'm not a fine-print God; I want to bless you.

00:29:24.240 --> 00:29:28.112
This isn't a trap.

00:29:28.112 --> 00:29:38.000
I love you, and I'm not looking to ensnare you.

00:29:38.000 --> 00:29:45.940
I'm not like your earthly father.

00:29:47.940 --> 00:29:56.519
My yes is yes, and My no is no.

00:29:56.519 --> 00:30:03.389
There's no gray with Me.

00:30:03.389 --> 00:30:11.290
Come before My throne boldly with grace.

00:30:11.290 --> 00:30:27.640
No good thing will He withhold from them who walk uprightly.

00:30:27.640 --> 00:30:54.219
' I forgot to tell you that at the beginning of this, I had a 4% battery and couldn't find a charger.

00:31:04.154 --> 00:31:11.760
I said, 'Lord, preserve my battery so I can write everything you're telling me.

00:31:11.760 --> 00:31:30.933
' He laughed and said, 'You come before My throne with such a small request, daughter.

00:31:30.933 --> 00:31:51.320
' I kept writing for over two hours, and when He finished talking, it was at 1%.

00:32:05.120 --> 00:32:05.629
God is amazing.

00:32:05.629 --> 00:32:25.056
He said, 'If you sync up with Me, you won't have to ask what the now word is.

00:32:25.056 --> 00:32:35.579
If you're asking, you've been out of sync for a while.

00:32:35.579 --> 00:32:42.778
I'm not a mean God; I'm focused.

00:32:42.778 --> 00:32:57.240
I know exactly what needs to happen, and I'm tired of having to explain myself.

00:32:57.240 --> 00:33:04.1000
Get in sync or come home to Me.

00:33:04.1000 --> 00:33:15.904
' I was thinking that sounded harsh, and He said, 'It's not harsh.

00:33:17.264 --> 00:33:25.400
They knew what I require of them, yet they offer excuses.

00:33:25.400 --> 00:33:32.879
I will not be mocked.

00:33:32.879 --> 00:33:49.124
' I asked why He was telling me all this, and He said, 'You asked what was on My heart today.

00:33:49.124 --> 00:34:03.939
' He said no one's perfect, but He's asking us to stay usable.

00:34:03.939 --> 00:34:15.440
'Don't come before My throne with excuses; I'm fed up with them.

00:34:15.440 --> 00:34:27.590
They tell Me what they aren't going to do and why; it's a stench.

00:34:27.590 --> 00:34:35.905
I am not a genie in a bottle.

00:34:35.905 --> 00:34:45.980
' Then He started talking about finances.

00:34:45.980 --> 00:34:58.812
He said if He can trust you, He will give more to you.

00:34:58.812 --> 00:35:09.680
If people withhold finances, it means they love money more than Him.

00:35:10.720 --> 00:35:19.396
He said, 'You passed the test with finances; I'm pleased.

00:35:19.396 --> 00:35:43.880
' I asked what I could do for Him, and He said, 'Stay in sync; don't become like them.

00:35:43.880 --> 00:36:05.149
' I asked if I could pray for them, and He said, 'Prayer is a sweet sound, but prayer won't change this.

00:36:05.149 --> 00:36:13.088
Their hearts are hardened in this area.

00:36:13.088 --> 00:36:30.307
' He's talking about ministers who have become callous and puffed up because of their platforms.

00:36:30.307 --> 00:36:43.382
They feel they are equal with Him or bigger than Him.

00:36:43.382 --> 00:37:03.540
They stop checking in because they think they already know what He's going to say.

00:37:13.857 --> 00:37:14.572
They put Him in a box and get out of sync.

00:37:14.572 --> 00:37:24.370
Don't become reliant on the gift; stay reliant on Me.

00:37:24.370 --> 00:37:47.680
When you start flowing in the Holy Spirit and seeing signs and wonders, don't stop spending time with Him every day.

00:37:47.680 --> 00:37:51.876
Without Him, who are we?

00:37:51.876 --> 00:37:58.312
Without prayer, who are you anyway?

00:37:58.312 --> 00:38:04.240
It must be a pillar.

00:38:10.470 --> 00:38:12.906
You must fear God more than man.

00:38:12.906 --> 00:38:23.580
Follow His leadings and promptings, and He's got your back.

00:38:26.215 --> 00:38:30.693
You work for Him; fear Him.

00:38:30.693 --> 00:38:51.860
I feel the bottom line is for the body of Christ to know that He's out of time.

00:39:02.151 --> 00:39:05.040
Jesus Christ is coming, and without His people yielding themselves, He cannot flow through them.

00:39:05.040 --> 00:39:30.590
It must be frustrating for God; He wants to get things done on Earth, but He deals with knuckleheads who say they're tired.

00:39:30.590 --> 00:39:54.130
He could appear as Elohim or Jehovah Jireh and say, 'I am God, get saved,' but He uses us.

00:39:54.130 --> 00:40:00.806
How bad do you want it?

00:40:00.806 --> 00:40:07.120
Do you want change or not?

00:40:07.120 --> 00:40:31.994
If He gives you a gift, are you going to hold it hostage or let Him use it for the greater purpose?

00:40:31.994 --> 00:40:41.159
Don't get a big head and think for Him.

00:40:41.159 --> 00:41:00.600
That's why He was correcting me about the Yankees—I was trying to think for Him.

00:41:00.600 --> 00:41:20.591
Don't hide yourself because you're intimidated or care too much about people's opinions.

00:41:20.591 --> 00:41:31.428
Stay in sync like the ticking of a clock.

00:41:31.428 --> 00:41:41.779
He knows exactly what you're supposed to do daily and hourly.

00:41:44.186 --> 00:41:48.559
The Bible says to pray without ceasing.

00:41:50.622 --> 00:42:04.307
The disciples were filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit because they sought Him hourly.

00:42:04.307 --> 00:42:18.020
Smith Wigglesworth was a great man of God who raised many from the dead.

00:42:18.020 --> 00:42:38.340
He carried an Old and New Testament in his pockets and would read them every 15 minutes to stay filled with the spirit.

00:42:38.340 --> 00:42:44.029
That's what it takes: being sold out.

00:42:44.029 --> 00:42:55.000
Have prayer as your foundation and don't give excuses.

00:42:55.000 --> 00:42:59.084
God is a bold God.

00:42:59.084 --> 00:43:10.920
We make things so religious, but even a child can follow Him.

00:43:10.920 --> 00:43:13.744
He's not looking to ensnare you.

00:43:13.744 --> 00:43:28.480
Can He use you like He did Billy Graham, Reinhard Bonnke, R.

00:43:28.480 --> 00:43:29.463
W.

00:43:29.463 --> 00:43:36.205
Schambach, Kenneth Hagin, or Jack Coe?

00:43:36.651 --> 00:43:56.599
It's one thing to ask to be used and another to submit yourself fully to the refiner's fire.

00:43:56.599 --> 00:44:20.040
I know beyond a shadow of a doubt that Jesus is coming, but He's not coming until He has His harvest.

00:44:20.040 --> 00:44:30.054
He's waiting for people like us to be the mouthpiece.

00:44:30.054 --> 00:44:48.415
Be quick to obey, whether it's witnessing in Walmart or helping someone with a tank of gas.

00:44:58.788 --> 00:45:16.261
You never know what someone is going through; they could be at their wit's end, and your obedience shows them the love of God.

00:45:16.261 --> 00:45:26.050
Diana bought tracts for us to keep in the car.

00:45:26.050 --> 00:45:55.759
When she was five, she found a box of witnessing cards and felt the Holy Spirit tell her to give one to a scary-looking guy on a motorcycle.

00:45:55.759 --> 00:46:02.755
She was trembling but told him, 'Jesus loves you.

00:46:02.755 --> 00:46:06.880
' That man started sobbing.

00:46:06.880 --> 00:46:10.699
It impacted her forever.

00:46:10.699 --> 00:46:16.465
Some plant, some water, and some harvest.

00:46:21.595 --> 00:46:30.337
The wheat crop is ready, and we're about to see signs and wonders like never before.

00:46:30.337 --> 00:46:34.933
Let's pray for the election.

00:46:35.227 --> 00:46:41.693
Father, we thank You for another day.

00:46:42.480 --> 00:46:53.459
We want this channel to be an oasis where people are refreshed.

00:47:02.355 --> 00:47:02.687
We see the urgency of the hour.

00:47:02.687 --> 00:47:12.333
We call forth the harvest in the name of Jesus.

00:47:27.554 --> 00:47:32.300
We speak to the coughs and drainage; we say we are healed and whole by Your stripes.

00:47:32.300 --> 00:47:52.920
We thank You for boldness to tell the good news that Jesus Christ died and rose again.

00:47:54.100 --> 00:48:05.537
We believe You raise the dead, cast out devils, and heal the blind.

00:48:07.340 --> 00:48:13.360
We believe for the restoration of households and marriages.

00:48:13.360 --> 00:48:17.600
We are God-conscious, not devil-conscious.

00:48:31.749 --> 00:48:32.019
You supply all our needs.

00:48:38.915 --> 00:48:47.860
We speak against PTSD, Alzheimer's, dementia, autism, cerebral palsy, and Crohn's.

00:48:47.860 --> 00:48:55.879
It is all under the blood.

00:48:59.794 --> 00:49:07.800
You took the crown of thorns so we don't have to have mental torment.

00:49:11.550 --> 00:49:17.862
For whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:49:18.307 --> 00:49:25.720
I plead the blood of Jesus over their minds.

00:49:25.720 --> 00:49:50.690
According to 2 Timothy 1:7, God has not given them a spirit of fear, but of power, love, and a well-balanced mind.

00:49:50.690 --> 00:49:57.099
We speak life over your bodies.

00:50:09.968 --> 00:50:10.232
We speak against addictions—drugs, alcohol, pornography.

00:50:10.232 --> 00:50:21.113
You came to set the captives free, and it is already done.

00:50:32.980 --> 00:50:35.371
We thank You that You are going to turn around the election.

00:50:47.720 --> 00:50:47.982
This will be a week of great victory.

00:50:47.982 --> 00:51:04.599
President Trump will be the next president, and we will have a red wave throughout this land.

00:51:17.920 --> 00:51:23.240
We thank You for favor with the judges, that they would rule by the law of the land and not bias.

00:51:23.240 --> 00:51:37.880
We thank You for Kari Lake, Ted Cruz, and all those running for office.

00:51:37.880 --> 00:51:52.193
We pray for revival throughout the world—over Asia, Israel, and peace over Jerusalem.

00:51:52.193 --> 00:52:03.091
We pray for the innocent lives in Palestine and protection over their children.

00:52:03.091 --> 00:52:18.545
We thank You that the Israeli people would rise up and take the land back.

00:52:19.670 --> 00:52:26.347
We call for an exposing of all rioting.

00:52:32.360 --> 00:52:34.667
I call for peace over this land and no terrorist attacks.

00:52:34.667 --> 00:52:41.173
We thank You for divine protection over polling areas.

00:52:41.173 --> 00:52:51.155
We believe God is not done with America yet.

00:52:51.155 --> 00:53:01.453
We pray over finances and thank You for the blessing on our homes.

00:53:01.453 --> 00:53:07.399
Rebuke the devourer for our sake.

00:53:07.399 --> 00:53:09.020
Everyone say amen.

00:53:09.020 --> 00:53:14.839
I'm thankful you came on today, babe.

00:53:17.080 --> 00:53:19.777
That word was powerful.

00:53:19.777 --> 00:53:29.799
Thank You, Lord, for speaking to my wife.

00:53:30.252 --> 00:53:41.134
If you're new here, we're taking off Cash App; we aren't going to use it anymore.

00:53:41.134 --> 00:53:50.700
PayPal and Venmo are fine, but we're going to use Zelle.

00:53:59.713 --> 00:54:00.079
We're also doing t-shirts as a witnessing tool.

00:54:00.079 --> 00:54:14.106
Let's make Christian t-shirts great again—not the cheesy ones you find at Mardel.

00:54:14.106 --> 00:54:22.119
We'll have coffee cups and sweatshirts in the link below.

00:54:22.119 --> 00:54:32.839
We also have tax-deductible donation options now for those who asked.

00:54:32.839 --> 00:54:36.249
We hit 400,000 subscribers!

00:54:36.249 --> 00:54:45.160
Subscribe if you haven't, and click the notification bell.

00:54:45.160 --> 00:54:54.171
We'll see you tomorrow for the election.

00:55:03.684 --> 00:55:10.160
We might do a live stream to watch the coverage together for an hour or two.

00:55:10.160 --> 00:55:26.300
I don't want to watch CNN or MSNBC; that'll make your hair fall out.

00:55:26.300 --> 00:55:38.651
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:55:38.651 --> 00:55:46.748
Jesus loves you and we love you.

00:55:46.748 --> 00:55:48.630
God bless you.

00:55:48.630 --> 00:55:49.390
Bye-bye.
